{"word":"G3960 - πατάσσω - patássō - pat-as'-so - Smite","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πατάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">patássō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pat-as'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Smite</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெட்டு, தட்டு, வாதி"},{"paragraph":"1. to strike gently"},{"paragraph":"2. to strike, smite"},{"paragraph":"3. to smite down, to cut down, to kill, to slay"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably a prolongation from <a href=\"#/G3817 - παίω - paíō - pah'-yo/3817\">G3817</a>; to <i>knock</i> (gently or with a weapon or fatally): - smite, strike. Compare <a href=\"#/G5180 - τύπτω - týptō - toop'-to/5180\">G5180</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}